            "id": 5969574,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉美英達成貿易協議 台積電噴漲2% 大漲逾百點站回5日線",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國總統川普昨 (8) 日晚間宣布，與英國達成「突破性」貿易協議，提振市場信心，激勵美股四大指數全面收紅，台積電 ADR 也上漲 0.39%，帶動台股今 (9) 日早盤漲逾百點，最高漲至 20762.38 點，站回 5 日線，預估成交量 2900 億元。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普聲稱，已與英國達成重大的貿易協議，英國對美國商品的平均關稅從 5.1% 降至 1.8%，並擴大美國商品的進口管道。不過英國出口至美國的商品，仍適用 10% 的基礎關稅。雖然相關協議細節尚未敲定，但值得注意的是，英國汽車關稅將降至 10%，農產品關稅更有望降為零。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美英達成貿易協議，為半導體關稅結果帶來希望，電子權值股今天幾乎全面勁揚，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 以 938 開出，漲逾 2%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 漲逾 1%，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 漲 0.78%，廣達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2382:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2382\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2382-TW</a>) 漲 0.6%，台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 漲 0.67%，日月光 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3711:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3711\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3711-TW</a>) 則於平盤附近遊走。不過金融雙雄今天表現弱勢，國泰金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2882:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2882\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2882-TW</a>)、富邦金 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2881:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2881\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2881-TW</a>) 雙雙跌逾 1% </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>航運族群今天也紅通通，貨櫃三雄表現亮眼，萬海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2615:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2615\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2615-TW</a>) 漲逾 2%，陽明 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2609:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2609\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2609-TW</a>)、長榮 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2603:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2603\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2603-TW</a>) 雙雙漲逾 1%。另外，台驊 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2636:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2636\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2636-TW</a>)、中航 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2612:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2612\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2612-TW</a>) 也都漲逾 1%。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美股四大指全數走揚，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>上漲 254.48 或 0.62%，收 41368.45 點；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">那斯達克</a>指數上漲 189.98 點或 1.07%，收 17928.14 點；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a> 指數上漲 32.66 點或 0.58%，收 5663.94 點；<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數上漲 44.08 點或 1%，收 4430.44 點。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
